data.text:
Proud to see North Dakota agriculture featured in @Budweiser’s #SuperBowlLX commercial with Coleharbor farmer Brian Fransen, reminding America where its barley comes from. 
https://t.co/eTepZhWtbW https://t.co/17QC5iJ6IG

Met with North Dakota representatives from Mid-States Organized Crime Information Center to discuss coordination and information sharing to support law enforcement officers & public safety in ND. https://t.co/HYTzWkK21K

Congrats to @NDSUPresident Cook and everyone who helped make @NDSUfootball’s move to the FBS and @MountainWest Conference a reality.

Best wishes to President Cook (aka the Big Bison) and his wife Kate at @IowaStateU - and thank you for all you’ve done for @NDSU.

PS… Bison vs. https://t.co/iu96wC3Ftx
Huge congratulations to former @NDSUfootball players @GreyZabel and Jalen Sundell on a @SuperBowl victory! A very proud moment for #BisonNation and North Dakota. #SuperBowlLX
Wishing former @NDSUfootball standouts @GreyZabel and #JalenSundell the best of luck as they compete in @SuperBowl LX today! Excited to see #BisonNation represented on football’s biggest stage.
